content.rendered:
Hi everyone!! My boyfriend, Bryce, and I did a couples tag together! I FINALLY got him to do a video with me (on Valentines day) hahah. We first answer some questions together, then go into matchup speed rounds to see how well we know each other. I hope you enjoy the video!!
Love,
Katie
Instagram @katie.austin
